==X射线源==

格利泽687是极少见的能发射X射线的[[紅矮星|紅矮星]]。<ref name=Schmitt>{{ cite journal |doi=10.1086/176149 |author=Schmitt JHMM, Fleming TA, Giampapa MS |title=The X-ray view of the low-mass stars in the solar neighborhood |journal=Ap J. |volume=450 |issue=9 |pages=392–400 |bibcode=1995ApJ...450..392S |date=September 1995}}</ref>

